{"tid":1323681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」黑色三毛警告","createTime":"2019-07-16T10:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T10:38:18.000Z","uid":184771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f11aad5ab66346a2abe03c3495b08abe6bf50954","tid":1323681,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"一時之間，連燈有好多前線分裂post、戒嚴post、解放軍落嚟香港post、舊新聞post、盧偉聰對話流出post、律師收好貴錢post。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而無集中討論721有咩行動方案。究竟係和理非散場定係做咩呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而今日，有連登仔運動有兩個睇法<br />\n一、就係七二一去金鐘；<br />\n二、就係金鐘行去銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n我無意批評，提出新方案嘅係人定係鬼，但懇請各方俾新建議嘅時候，提出一個具體嘅方案。<br />\n<br />\n方案各有有壞<br />\n一、金鐘孤島，但多政府機構，遊行示威係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">施壓</span></span>（大家自行解讀）<br />\n二、銅鑼灣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">易逃走</span></span>（壓倒性優勢），但無象徵機構，遊行示威目的在那？<br />\n<br />\n因此，大家不要只顧推post，討論下兩達地方點，點樣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">調和好壞</span></span>"},{"pid":"0017695243ed7a6bcad0a8994422054f08f4834d","tid":1323681,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"如水"},{"pid":"53612c3fbc4892b23ae6c6a4b6b5bb2d18f44acc","tid":1323681,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"大家拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"53676877f6c0e7e5b02392fa6a2432520b0fe47f","tid":1323681,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"大家拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"9e453f524128865f92fa79d0f20ac1be8d6a4344","tid":1323681,"uid":184771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"大家拋磚引玉"}]}